---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Jinit Shah"
  description="Jinit Shah — senior software engineer and mathematician merging the elegance of math with the creativity of code. Strong advocate for explainable AI, and data ownership and privacy."
  current="/"
  headerOn="dark"
>
  <section class="section theme-black-bold" data-hero>
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <figure class="hero-photo">
        <img
          src="/img/profile.jpeg"
          width="1830"
          height="2067"
          alt="Jinit Shah"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </figure>
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h4 class="hero-hey">Hey, <span class="hey-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span></h4>
        <h2>
          I’m a <strong><em>senior software developer</em></strong> and a
          <strong><em>mathematician</em></strong>, deeply passionate and curious about finding
          solutions to intricate problems. Merging the elegance of math with the creativity of
          code, one day, I hope to make the world a better place!
        </h2>
        <h2>Strong advocate for explainable AI, and data ownership and privacy.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black">
    <div class="section__inner awards" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="award">
        <img src="/img/duck.png" width="360" height="360" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        <p>
          Received <strong>#1 Place Capstone Award in VTURCS</strong> (Virginia Tech Undergraduate
          Research in Computer Science)
        </p>
        <p>For <a href="/experience">GYD (Graph Your Data)</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="award">
        <img src="/img/duck.png" width="360" height="360" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        <p><strong>Won Kickstart VT</strong></p>
        <p>Hosted by Apex Center for Entrepreneurs - Virginia Tech</p>
        <p>For <a href="/passion">Handsway</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-light-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="feature-meta">
        <h1 class="handsway-title">
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/handsway/id1641972653" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Handsway</a>
        </h1>
        <p>Personal Project</p>
        <p><em>Launched: February 2022</em></p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>
          Handsway is a one-of-a-kind, completely free (and will always remain free), mobile
          application that uses machine learning to translate ASL signs to text from your phone
          camera in real time. Handsway has received <strong>$4K+ in funding</strong> and helped
          <strong>2k+ users</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="dream-build" data-reveal-group>
          <div>
            <h4>Dream it.</h4>
            <p>
              I’ve always been fascinated by sign languages and had a life-long dream to learn
              them. However, while learning ASL, upon curious investigation I discovered there
              weren’t any apps that could translate ASL to text in real time. Since 500K+ people
              rely on ASL just in the US &amp; Canada, I recognized a substantial need to break the
              communication barrier between them and people who don’t understand ASL.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Build it.</h4>
            <p>
              Knowing the importance of something like this, I had to do something about it.
              However, the most challenging part was to find an extensive public dataset. So, to
              make this app possible I had asked my friends and family to provide me with videos of
              them doing ASL. To speed up this process and add variability in my dataset, you can
              also help Handsway grow faster.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
